Name: Catbusters
About the game: Catbusters is an action-packed multiplayer wave shooter for Steam VR. You must defend against Count Scratchula and his evil undead minions. You are a mighty Catbusters armed with high-tech weapons to battle the hoards of vampire cats. Can you survive the fury of the furball attacks? Features Cooperative multiplayer action Exciting weapon bonuses Big boss challenges Selectable difficulty levels
